Package: corek
Title: Personalized K-Factor Axis for Text Feature Spaces
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Kathrin", "Preuss", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "not-public@example.com")
Author: Kathrin Preuss
Maintainer: Kathrin Preuss <not-public@example.com>
Description: Fits a personalized K-Factor axis in a PCA-transformed text-feature
    space and scores new texts by projection, normalized axis position and
    orthogonal distance. The package contains the method, not private reference
    data, proprietary model bundles or forensic thresholds.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    plotly,
    htmlwidgets,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
